‚úÖ 1. Login API
URL: /api/v1/auth/login
Method: POST

Request Body:
{
  "username": "user@example.com",
  "password": "yourPassword"
}

Response (200 OK):
{
  "accessToken": "jwt-token",
  "refreshToken": "refresh-token",
  "username": "user@example.com",
  "roles": ["ROLE_USER"]
}

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 2. Register API
URL: /api/v1/auth/register
Method: POST

Request Body:
{
  "username": "user@example.com",
  "password": "yourPassword",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "phone": "1234567890"
}

Response (200 OK):
{
  "message": "User registered successfully",
  "userId": "123"
}

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 3. Validate JWT Token
URL: /api/v1/auth/validateToken
Method: POST

Query Parameter:
token=your.jwt.token

Response (200 OK):
{
  "valid": true
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 4. Forgot Password
URL: /api/v1/auth/forgot
Method: POST

Request Body:
{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

Response (200 OK):
{
  "message": "Password reset link sent to email"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 5. Reset Password
URL: /api/v1/auth/reset
Method: POST

Request Body:
{
  "token": "reset-token-from-email",
  "newPassword": "newSecurePassword"
}

Response (200 OK):
{
  "message": "Password has been reset successfully"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 6. Get Current User Profile
URL: /api/v1/users/profile
Method: GET
Auth: ‚úÖ Required (any authenticated user)

Response (200 OK):
{
  "userId": 1,
  "username": "johndoe",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "profileImageUrl": "http://.../profile/image/xyz.jpg"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 7. Update Current User Profile
URL: /api/v1/users/profile

Method: PUT

Content-Type: multipart/form-data

Auth: ‚úÖ Required

Request Parts:

profile: ProfileUpdateDTO (JSON)

image: MultipartFile (optional)
{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}
Response (200 OK): Same as Get Profile

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 8. Delete User by ID
URL: /api/v1/users/{userId}

Method: DELETE

Auth: ‚úÖ Required

Response (204 No Content): No body

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 9. Get Profile Image
URL: /api/v1/users/profile/image/{fileName}

Method: GET

Auth: ‚ùå Not Required

Response (200 OK): Image (Content-Type: image/jpeg)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

