  "phone": "1234567890"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 11. Get All Users (Paginated)
URL: /api/v1/users

Method: GET

Query Params:

includeInactive (boolean, default: false)

page (int)

size (int)

Auth: ‚úÖ Required (Role: ADMIN)

Response (200 OK):
{
  "content": [
    {
      "userId": 1,
      "username": "johndoe",
      ...
    }
  ],
  "totalPages": 5,
  "totalElements": 100,
  "number": 0,
  "size": 20
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 12. Get User by ID
URL: /api/v1/users/{id}

Method: GET

Auth: ‚úÖ Required (ADMIN only)

Response (200 OK): UserDTO

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 13. Create New User
URL: /api/v1/users

Method: POST

Body:
{
  "username": "newuser",
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "new@example.com",
  "phone": "1234567890",
  "password": "securePass123"
}

Response (201 Created):
{
  "userId": 123,
  "username": "newuser",
  ...
}
Location Header: /api/users/123

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 14. Update Existing User
URL: /api/v1/users/{id}

Method: PUT

Auth: ‚úÖ Required (ADMIN only)

Body: Same as Create User

Response (200 OK): Updated UserDTO

