‚úÖ 22. Create Restaurant
URL: /api/v1/restaurants

Method: POST

Request Body (RestaurantDTO):
{
  "name": "Spice Villa",
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "description": "Authentic Indian cuisine",
  "imageUrl": null
}

Response (201 Created):
{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Spice Villa",
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "description": "Authentic Indian cuisine",
  "imageUrl": "http://.../restaurants/images/spice-villa.jpg"
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 23. Get All Restaurants (Paginated)
URL: /api/v1/restaurants

Method: GET

Query Parameters:

page: Page number (required)

size: Page size (required)

keyword: Search keyword (optional)

Response (200 OK):
{
  "content": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Spice Villa",
      "address": "123 Main Street",
      "description": "Authentic Indian cuisine",
      "imageUrl": "http://.../restaurants/images/spice-villa.jpg"
    },
    ...
  ],
  "totalPages": 5,
  "totalElements": 100,
  "number": 0,
  "size": 20
}

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

‚úÖ 24. Upload Restaurant Image
URL: /api/v1/restaurants/{restaurantId}/upload-image

Method: POST

Content-Type: multipart/form-data

Form Data:

file: MultipartFile (image file)

Response (200 OK):
{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Spice Villa",
  "address": "123 Main Street",
  "description": "Authentic Indian cuisine",
  "imageUrl": "http://.../restaurants/images/spice-villa.jpg"
}
404 Not Found: If restaurant not found

